217
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:01,240
  I'm in love, I'm in love with a girl 
 in India.

218
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:06,920
  And who is she? 
A younger woman, of course.

219
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:11,080
  Well, I'm not old, you know? 
 My life isn't over not by any means.

220
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:12,120
  Well, you of course ...

221
