think me as a failure, 
 wich I suppose I am compared to all that.

222
00:26:15,120 --> 00:26:17,040
  But who is she? Tell me.

223
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:23,000
  A married woman. 
 Unfortunately.

224
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:26,240
  She's the wife of a major 
 in the Indian Army.

225
